data.description: POSSIBLE ASSUMABLE 2.75% FHA Loan with an amazingly low monthly payment - Contact me for more information.  Immaculately maintained residence located in a sought-after Veneta neighborhood. This home boasts an extremely popular open floor plan that offers a perfect balance of space and privacy, highlighted by a separation of the primary bedroom area. The interior features elegant vaulted ceilings, recently upgraded flooring, spacious his and her closets in the primary bedroom, a convenient indoor laundry room, and a state-of-the-art heat pump with an active warranty. Step outside to discover a vast covered patio, ideal for outdoor gatherings. Every corner of this home reflects a genuine sense of ownership pride.
